RELEASE NOTES for BANDIT
========================

This is the release "1.6.0" of the BANDIT toolkit.
This is a "STABLE" release.

See https://docs.phyglos.org/bandit for more information.


MAJOR CHANGES in "1.6.0"
=========================

* Added new command to deal with alien items in a bundle
* Added aliens-latest catalog in bandit.conf
* Allow to search repositories with an expression
* Allow to search catalogs with an expression


